*Telecom Customer Churn Analysis*

Analysis of 7,043 telecom customers to identify churn patterns and revenue retention opportunities using SQL.

*Insights*
- Month-to-month contract customers churn at 42.7% (15X higher than two-year contract customers (2.8%))
- Â£1.45M in annual revenue at risk from month-to-month customer churn alone.
- Contract type is the strongest predictor of customer retention.
- One-year contracts show moderate churn (11.3%), suggesting mid-term commitments balance flexibility and retention.

